title: Josefine Krengel
text: Josefine Krengel is a German <a href="women%27s%20soccer">football</a> <a href="defender%20%28soccer%29">defender</a>, currently playing for <a href="1.FC%20Lokomotive%20Leipzig%20%28women%29">Lokomotive Leipzig</a> in the <a href="Frauen%20Bundesliga">Bundesliga</a>. She previously played for <a href="Turbine%20Potsdam">Turbine Potsdam</a>, <a href="FC%20Bayern%20Munich%20%28women%29">Bayern Munich</a> and <a href="Tennis%20Borussia%20Berlin%20%28women%29">Tennis Borussia Berlin</a>.
